## No File Duplication

- **NEVER** create `file-simple.ts`, `file-v2.ts`, `file-enhanced.ts` variants
- **ALWAYS** edit existing files directly using search_replace
- **NEVER** create parallel implementations

## Standards

- Read full file context before changes
- Preserve existing functionality when adding features
- Maintain production-grade quality - not prototypes
- Keep complex logic when it serves a purpose
